Example source: [medasr-ctc-c-api.c](https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx/blob/master/c-api-examples/medasr-ctc-c-api.c)

@section offline_asr_telespeech TeleSpeech CTC

TeleSpeech is a Chinese CTC model. Note the simple string assignment
for the model path.

@code
config.model_config.telespeech_ctc =
    "./sherpa-onnx-telespeech-ctc-int8-zh-2024-06-04/model.int8.onnx";
config.model_config.tokens =
    "./sherpa-onnx-telespeech-ctc-int8-zh-2024-06-04/tokens.txt";
@endcode

Model package: `sherpa-onnx-telespeech-ctc-int8-zh-2024-06-04`

Example source: [telespeech-c-api.c](https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx/blob/master/c-api-examples/telespeech-c-api.c)
